---
title: Tourongo — All Authentication Flows
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as Spring Boot :8081
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant GOOGLE as Google OAuth2
    participant EMAIL as Brevo SMTP

    rect rgb(200, 240, 210)
        Note over U,EMAIL: Flow 1 — Email Registration (3-step signup)
        U->>FE: Step 1: Choose role (Traveler / Guide)
        U->>FE: Step 2: Fill name, email, password
        U->>FE: Step 3: Accept Terms + Privacy
        FE->>API: POST /api/auth/register {role, name, email, password, agreedTerms, agreedPrivacy}
        API->>DB: INSERT user (emailVerified=false, hasPassword=true, profileCompleted=false)
        API->>EMAIL: Send 6-digit verification code (30min TTL)
        API-->>FE: {accessToken, user}
        FE->>FE: Store accessToken, set HttpOnly refresh cookie
        FE->>FE: Show onboarding banner (verify email + complete profile)
    end

    rect rgb(200, 215, 255)
        Note over U,GOOGLE: Flow 2 — Google OAuth2 Login
        U->>FE: Click "Continue with Google"
        FE->>API: GET /oauth2/authorize/google
        API->>GOOGLE: Redirect to Google consent screen
        GOOGLE-->>API: GET /login/oauth2/code/google?code=...
        API->>GOOGLE: Exchange code → {email, name, picture}
        API->>DB: Upsert user (hasPassword=false for new OAuth users)
        API->>FE: Redirect /auth/oauth-callback?token=...
        FE->>FE: Extract token, store in AuthContext
        Note over FE: OAuth users see "Set Password" option in settings
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 200)
        Note over U,API: Flow 3 — Token Refresh (auto-silent)
        FE->>API: Any request → 401 Unauthorized
        FE->>FE: Queue all concurrent 401s
        FE->>API: POST /api/auth/refresh (HttpOnly cookie auto-sent)
        API->>DB: Validate + rotate refresh token
        API-->>FE: New accessToken + new refresh cookie
        FE->>FE: Retry ALL queued requests with new token
    end

    rect rgb(240, 200, 255)
        Note over U,EMAIL: Flow 4 — Password Reset
        U->>FE: Click "Forgot Password"
        FE->>API: POST /api/auth/password/forgot {email}
        API->>EMAIL: 6-digit code, 15min TTL
        U->>FE: Enter code + new password
        FE->>API: POST /api/auth/password/reset {token, newPassword}
        API->>DB: Update password hash, invalidate token
        API-->>FE: Success
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 200)
        Note over U,EMAIL: Flow 5 — OAuth User Sets Password
        U->>FE: Settings → "Set Password" → request code
        FE->>API: POST /api/auth/password/setup/request
        API->>EMAIL: 6-digit code, 15min TTL
        U->>FE: Enter code + desired password
        FE->>API: POST /api/auth/password/setup/confirm {code, newPassword}
        API->>DB: Set password_hash, hasPassword=true
        API-->>FE: Success (user can now login with email+password)
    end

    rect rgb(200, 255, 240)
        Note over U,EMAIL: Flow 6 — Email Verification
        FE->>API: POST /api/auth/email/verify/request
        API->>EMAIL: 6-digit code, 30min TTL
        U->>FE: Enter 6-digit code
        FE->>API: POST /api/auth/email/verify/confirm-code {code}
        API->>DB: SET emailVerified=true
        API->>DB: INSERT notification (EMAIL_VERIFIED)
        API-->>FE: Success, onboarding step cleared
    end
